OL,5, The typical household energy bill is   
OL,6, set to rise by about #800 a year in    
OL,7, October, the energy regulator warns.   
OL,9,FOfgem boss Jonathan Brearley said the  
OL,10,Fenergy price cap, which limits how much
OL,11,Fproviders can raise prices, is expected
OL,12,Fto increase to #2,800 a year, due to   
OL,13,Fcontinued volatility in gas prices.    
OL,15,FMr Brearley said the price rises were a
OL,16,F"once in a generation event not seen   
OL,17,Fsince the oil crisis in the 1970s".    
OL,19,FHe also said the number of people in   
OL,20,Ffuel poverty may double to 12 million. 
